<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM9.6">
<l>ammāveṉ ṟukantaḻaikku mārvaccoṟ kēḷātē yaṇicēr mārvam</l>
<l>eṉmārvat tiṭaiyaḻuntat taḻuvātē muḻucātē mōvā tuccik</l>
<l>kaimmāviṉ ṉaṭaiyaṉṉa meṉṉaṭaiyuṅ kamalampōl mukamuṅ kāṇātu</l>
<l>emmāṉai yeṉmakaṉai yiḻantiṭṭa viḻittakaiyē ṉirukkiṉ ṟēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, who am of an inferior character, [still] live,</l>
<l>[I] who have lost our Lord, my Son,</l>
<l rend="indent">[even] without hearing the affectionate word of [His] rejoicingly calling [me] ‘Father!’</l>
<l rend="indent">without embracing [Him] so that His bejewelled chest is pressed against my chest,</l>
<l rend="indent">without having been close [with Him],</l>
<l rend="indent">without smelling the crown of [His] head,</l>
<l rend="indent">without seeing [His] gentle gait [that is] like the gait of an elephant</l>
<l rend="indent"> [and His] lotus-like face.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
